1002610.1000851.1000867.1000976.type=PIO 1002610.1000851.1000867.1000973.description=Toyota trucks and off-road racing are tough. One of the toughest races of them all is the infamous Baja 1000. Give your Tacoma some of that toughness with a set of 6-spoke Baja alloy wheels:
•Lighter than comparable steel wheels - helps heat dissipation, enhances handling and improves braking performance
•Provide the proper weight, offset and brake clearance for a perfect fit
•Available in two colors: black and graphite

16-in. performance tires are often expected to experience greater tire wear than conventional tires. Tire life may be substantially less than mileage expectancy, depending upon tires used and driving conditions. 1002610.1000851.1000867.source=MANUAL_IMPORT 1002610.1000851.1000867.1000977.type=PIO 1002610.title= 1002610.1000851.1000867.1000974.description=Toyota trucks and off-road racing are tough.
